metadata.name: Barzen
metadata.description:
In a corner of the universe there was a galaxy called Barzen.
  It had been a long time since the light had defeated the darkness on this galaxy  But in an unreachable corner and far from the mind, the darkness rose again, but this time more powerful than any other time.  Once again strife and conflict covered the surface of the galaxy.
  Most of the galaxy was reduced to eternal nothingness.  The center of the galaxy was Ario Tower, which was surrounded by dark forces.  The light rose again to defeat the darkness, but it was too late...
